cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.NE 

The paper involves using reinforcement learning agents as generative models of images, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The agents are trained to produce realistic images, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves controlling a simulated painting environment, which falls under computer graphics (cs.GR). Finally, the use of reinforcement learning agents involves neural networks (cs.NE).
